            "component": {
              "name": "Copy",
              "options": {
                "rawHtml": "<p><strong>Highlights</strong></p><ul><li><em>Solana Mobile recently used Helio‚Äôs Solana Pay x Shopify plugin to support the release of their Chapter 2 mobile device ‚Äî and saved over $1,000,000 in fees compared to traditional payment methods.</em></li><li><em>The Solana Pay x Shopify plugin is managed by Helio, a Solana-first web3 payments platform that makes it easier to accept crypto payments.</em></li><li><em>The plugin merges the speed and efficiency of crypto payments with Shopify‚Äôs extensive market and offers low-fee, fast, real-time settlements in USDC, a stablecoin on Solana.</em></li><li><em>Over 200 Shopify stores adopted the plugin within three months of launch.</em></li><li><em>Helio is taking the plugin forward by focusing on support of more tokens and advanced web3 features such as token gating and NFT receipts.</em></li></ul>"
              }
            },
            "responsiveStyles": {
              "large": {
