              "name": "Copy",
              "options": {
                "rawHtml": "<p>\n  Using the\n  <a\n    href=\"https://apps.shopify.com/solana-pay\"\n    rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    >app</a\n  >, which requires minimal setup on the\n  <a\n    href=\"https://merchant.solanapay.com/\"\n    rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    >merchant portal</a\n  >, web2 and web3 businesses can quickly set up payments on Solana. Merchants\n  can track transactions, issue refunds, integrate with the Shopify product\n  delivery flow, and more by using the dashboard.\n</p>\n"
