                "content": "<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-dnt=\"true\" align=\"center\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">We did 20m+ in <a href=\"https://twitter.com/solanamobile?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@solanamobile</a> sales with <a href=\"https://twitter.com/Shopify?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@Shopify</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/solana?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@solana</a> usdc, paid $0 fees. The credit card sales cost us over $600k in fees on about the same volume. That‚Äôs 3 full time engineers. ü§Øü§Øü§Ø<br><br>Thanks <a href=\"https://t.co/nkwFCxI4hD\">https://t.co/nkwFCxI4hD</a>!!!<a href=\"https://t.co/tUtEm3Y3N9\">https://t.co/tUtEm3Y3N9</a></p>&mdash; toly üá∫üá∏ (@aeyakovenko) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/aeyakovenko/status/1757470276332450030?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">February 13, 2024</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n\n"
